screen_desc: The screenshot shows a mobile app interface for adding a payment method. The screen title is "Add payment." There are two options available: "Credit or Debit Card" with an icon of a card, and "Gift Card" with an icon of the Uber logo. The back arrow at the top left corner indicates the option to return to the previous screen. The status bar at the top shows the time as 8:34 AM, along with various status icons for notifications, battery, and connectivity.
